metadata.name: BrawlerZ Rampant Curse, Field Mission Day 1.
metadata.description:
A Curse has been spreading across the BrawlerZ Kingdom, 120 citizens (that we now know as Explorers) have departed on a mission beyon the Ice Clan Land to find the source of the Curse.

This is a picture is a snapshot of the first day of the mission.

You can follow BrawlerZ story line in this Twitter Moment: https://twitter.com/i/events/1545581239650091008

You can message @GTheGarden on Twitter to include your BrawlerZ in the picture.
